---
title: Teriyaki Chicken & Quick Corn Rice with Garlicky Baby Broccoli & Lime
description: Sweet, sticky and full of zing! This teriyaki chicken brings the flavour, teamed with speedy corn rice, punchy garlicky greens and a hit of lime and coriander to keep things fresh and fabulous.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
